text: Oswichee Creek is a stream in the U.S. state of Georgia. It is a tributary to the Chattahoochee River. Oswichee was the name of a tribe of the indigenous peoples of the Southeastern Woodlands. A variant spelling is "Oswitchee Creek". ==References== Category:Rivers of Georgia (U.S. state) Category:Bodies of water of Chattahoochee County, Georgia
title: Oswichee Creek
